description: *$50k Price Drop!* Elevate your lifestyle in this '19 built luxury 3 bed & 2.5 bath condo! Take the elevator from your 2 garage spaces to your exclusive 3rd level home. The open floor plan offers a wicked living room including a beautiful gas fireplace, a cook's kitchen with shaker cabinets, white quartz countertops, Sub-Zero & Wolf appliances, wine fridge, 4-seat island for casual dining & ½ bath. All of this leads to an incredible 20x10 Azek outdoor deck perfect for the outdoor season. Enjoy the oversized primary suite with blackout shades, walk-in closet, luxurious shower stall bath, rainfall shower, double vanity & heated floors. 2 additional queen-sized bedrooms, custom window treatments, ample closets, central AC & in-unit w/d. The heated garage offers side-by-side parking & private storage. 3 units, all owner occupied & self-managed assoc. with low HOA. Located on a quiet street at the corner of Broadway & Dorchester, you are but a hop, skip & a jump to all the Southie action.
